{"id": "art-456", "label": "Art. 456", "title": "Art. 456: Cererea de revizuire", "slug": "art-456", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1372026369\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1496\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1372026369\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 456: Cererea\nde revizuire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_145368176\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1495\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_145368176\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cererea de revizuire se adreseaz&#259; instan&#355;ei\ncare a judecat cauza în prima instan&#355;&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_959353603\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1494\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_959353603\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cererea se formuleaz&#259; în scris &#351;i trebuie\nmotivat&#259;, cu ar&#259;tarea cazului de revizuire pe care se întemeiaz&#259;\n&#351;i a mijloacelor de prob&#259; în dovedirea acestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1582701687\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1493\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1582701687\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La cerere se vor al&#259;tura copii de pe înscrisurile\nde care cel ce a formulat cererea de revizuire în&#355;elege a se folosi în\nproces, certificate pentru conformitate cu originalul. Când înscrisurile sunt\nredactate într-o limb&#259; str&#259;in&#259;, ele se vor al&#259;tura în\ntraducere efectuat&#259; de un traduc&#259;tor autorizat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2047703472\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1492\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2047703472\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care cererea nu îndepline&#351;te\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (2) &#351;i (3), instan&#355;a pune în\nvedere celui ce a formulat cererea s&#259; o completeze, într-un termen\nstabilit de instan&#355;&#259;, sub sanc&#355;iunea prev&#259;zut&#259; la art.\n459 alin. (5).</span></p>"}